'''2.0.154-dev''' ([[wikipedia:Microsoft Windows|Windows]]), or '''2.1.153-dev''' ([[wikipedia:macOS|macOS]]) is a version of the [[Minecraft launcher|launcher]].

== Additions ==
* First beta version of the new launcher.
* It is now possible to play the game with 2 accounts simultaneously.
